Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.57,0:01:00.20,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz26.62\pos(428,374)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.45,0:01:02.12,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz26.62\pos(320,420)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.45,0:01:02.12,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz26.62\pos(508,722)}创意总监
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.45,0:01:02.12,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.35,0:01:09.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道你是怎么做出来的  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.35,0:01:09.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know how you do it, Gar Bear
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.56,0:01:12.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是我喝过最棒的一杯法式吐司
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.56,0:01:12.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But that's the best cup of French toast I've ever had
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.34,0:01:16.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该去上班打卡了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.34,0:01:16.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, time to punch that clock
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.53,0:01:17.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过上班前得先看看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.53,0:01:17.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But not before checking
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.72,0:01:20.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的每日激励鸡汤日历
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.72,0:01:20.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my motivational quote-a-day calendar
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.35,0:01:22.43,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(906,314)}你是大赢家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.35,0:01:22.43,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\pos(824,816)}6{\fnAdobe 黑体 Std R}月{\fnArial}21{\fnAdobe 黑体 Std R}日  夏天的第一天
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.95,0:01:22.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是大赢家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.95,0:01:22.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"You are a winner"
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.54,0:01:29.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天还是夏天的第一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.54,0:01:29.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And today's the first day of summer
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.86,0:01:34.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,夏天的第一天快乐  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.86,0:01:34.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happy first day of summer, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.57,0:01:37.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不要一起来唱夏至颂歌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.57,0:01:37.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Care to join me for solstice caroling?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.02,0:01:38.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走在草地上  真晴朗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.02,0:01:38.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Walking in the grass, it's all fine
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.80,0:01:40.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,夏天里来不用穿鞋子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.80,0:01:40.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't need shoes in the summertime
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.43,0:01:48.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可不怎么喜欢夏天  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.43,0:01:48.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not much of a summer person, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.94,0:01:50.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的老天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.94,0:01:50.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Davy Jones on the jib
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.58,0:01:52.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没听错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.58,0:01:52.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do my ears deceive me?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.21,0:01:54.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天真是夏天的第一天吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.21,0:01:54.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is it really the first day of summer?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.86,0:01:55.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.86,0:01:55.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.78,0:01:56.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.78,0:01:56.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.19,0:02:03.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  你肯定患上了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.19,0:02:03.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gee, Mr. K, you sure have
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.06,0:02:05.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很严重的夏天热
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:05.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a scorching case of summer fever
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.02,0:02:06.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,夏日究竟有何物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.02,0:02:06.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is it about summertime
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.52,0:02:08.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能让我们如此开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.52,0:02:08.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that makes us so happy?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.01,0:02:09.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是萤火虫点亮的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.01,0:02:09.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The firefly-lit nights?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.61,0:02:12.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是木炭煤球醉人的芳香
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.61,0:02:12.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The intoxicating aroma of a charcoal briquette?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.47,0:02:15.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是割草机碾上拖鞋的助眠声响呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.47,0:02:14.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The hypnotic sound of a lawn mower
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.48,0:02:15.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,running over a flip-flop?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.74,0:02:17.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是钱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.74,0:02:17.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The money
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.31,0:02:18.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.31,0:02:18.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The money?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.13,0:02:20.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.13,0:02:20.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.11,0:02:21.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.11,0:02:21.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the children
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.85,0:02:22.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道吗  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.85,0:02:22.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You see, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.95,0:02:23.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,夏天的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.95,0:02:23.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,during the summer
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.72,0:02:25.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小孩子都不用上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.72,0:02:25.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the children are excused from their classes
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.80,0:02:29.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这段休息的时间通常被称作暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.80,0:02:29.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A recess commonly referred to as summer break
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.56,0:02:33.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多告诉我点暑假的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.56,0:02:33.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tell me more about summer break
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.29,0:02:35.09,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(304,548)}裤头村学校
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.57,0:02:35.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,暑假的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.57,0:02:35.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, during the summer break
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.10,0:02:38.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小孩子就会没人管  到裤头村到处逛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.10,0:02:38.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the children wander Bikini Bottom unsupervised
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.17,0:02:40.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且口袋里装满了零花钱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.17,0:02:40.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,their pockets lined with allowance
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.66,0:02:41.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爱怎么花就怎么花
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.66,0:02:41.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,free to spend their money
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.91,0:02:44.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,家长什么的根本管不着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.91,0:02:44.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,without any parental guidance whatsoever
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.06,0:02:48.56,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(936,550)}儿童餐
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.24,0:02:47.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那种事情我最喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.24,0:02:47.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess that's what I like best
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.58,0:02:50.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过肯定会有谁会想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.58,0:02:50.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure I suppose some would try
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.52,0:02:52.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,借此机会大捞一笔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.52,0:02:52.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and take advantage of this situation
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.16,0:02:55.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给他们兜售玩具或者糖果
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.16,0:02:55.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,by selling them toys or candy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.38,0:02:58.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是有这么一件事  能让我高枕无忧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.38,0:02:58.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I sleep well at night with the knowledge
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.48,0:03:00.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就是我可以给小孩子提供必需品
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.48,0:03:00.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that I'm providing them with something they need
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.22,0:03:02.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,营养大餐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.22,0:03:02.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A nutritious meal
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.26,0:03:05.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快过来  你们这些小猪崽子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.26,0:03:05.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come here, you little piggies
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.43,0:03:08.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我学到夏天的真谛了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.43,0:03:08.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've been taught the true meaning of summer
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.29,0:03:09.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,之后
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.35,0:03:12.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就快关门了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.35,0:03:12.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Almost closing time, Mr. K
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.60,0:03:13.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.60,0:03:13.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.67,0:03:15.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是不可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,0:03:15.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But that's impossible
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.23,0:03:16.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钱可怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.23,0:03:16.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What about the money?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.17,0:03:18.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.17,0:03:18.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.90,0:03:21.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小孩子怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.90,0:03:21.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What about the children?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.61,0:03:25.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来今年夏天来不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.61,0:03:25.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess summer isn't coming this year
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.66,0:03:27.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小朋友应该都在那边新修的游乐场里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.66,0:03:27.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe they're all at that new playground over there
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.16,0:03:28.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,游乐场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.16,0:03:28.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Playground?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.58,0:03:31.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把我的小客人们都给引走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.58,0:03:31.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Luring away me young customers?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.43,0:03:33.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,发动汽船  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.43,0:03:33.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Warm up the boat, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.46,0:03:39.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看见什么了吗  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.46,0:03:39.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See anything, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.84,0:03:42.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们就在这
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.84,0:03:42.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're here all right
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.35,0:03:44.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看他们  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.35,0:03:44.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just look at them, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.41,0:03:46.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多么脆弱  多么营养不良
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:46.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So weak and malnourished
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.73,0:03:49.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还没人给他们卖东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.73,0:03:49.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with nobody trying to sell them nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.12,0:03:50.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太伤我心了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:50.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Breaks me heart
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.00,0:03:57.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:03:57.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.32,0:04:00.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我生活都失去目的了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.32,0:04:00.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got nothing to live for, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.99,0:04:02.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你都能一边开船
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.99,0:04:02.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The way you drove the boat
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.44,0:04:04.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一边躺地上了  还算是有点酷的了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.44,0:04:04.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,while lying on the ground was kind of cool
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.53,0:04:06.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.53,0:04:06.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,True
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.49,0:04:08.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可那样还是没法让这些小屁孩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.49,0:04:08.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But that's not going to get these munchkins
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.12,0:04:09.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,离开这游乐场
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.12,0:04:09.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,away from this playground
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.75,0:04:11.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,除非
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.75,0:04:11.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Unless
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.58,0:04:14.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明天见  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.58,0:04:14.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.57,0:04:15.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得去干一堆活呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.57,0:04:15.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Got a lot of work to do
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.88,0:04:17.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没问题  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.88,0:04:17.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got it, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.30,0:04:20.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新的一天也要赚钱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.30,0:04:20.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Another day, another dollar
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.13,0:04:23.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知蟹老板干了啥活  自上次见到他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.13,0:04:23.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gee, I wonder what Mr. Krabs has been up to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.11,0:04:23.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,since I saw him last
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.91,0:04:25.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,过后我就回家无所事事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.91,0:04:24.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and then went home
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:25.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to do nothing of particular interest
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.93,0:04:26.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一直到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.93,0:04:26.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,till this very moment
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:28.62,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(372,868)}蟹堡乐园  欢腾一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:31.66,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(400,508)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.39,0:04:34.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.39,0:04:34.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.61,0:04:37.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你来得正好  现在要来盛大揭幕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.61,0:04:37.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're just in time for the grand unveiling of
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.59,0:04:39.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:39.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby Land
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.08,0:04:40.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡乐园吗  老板
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.08,0:04:40.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby Land, sir?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.50,0:04:42.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  蟹堡乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.50,0:04:42.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Krabby Land
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:44.84,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(480,856)}蟹堡乐园
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.74,0:04:44.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小孩子可以在这大玩特玩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.74,0:04:44.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where a kid can have fun
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.07,0:04:46.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且价格公道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.07,0:04:46.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For the right price
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.45,0:04:50.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临蟹堡王  小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:50.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Krusty Krab, young man
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.01,0:04:51.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.01,0:04:51.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.07,0:04:51.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,梦露
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.07,0:04:51.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Monroe
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.89,0:04:53.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很高兴认识你  梦露
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:53.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, Monroe
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.61,0:04:59.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  钱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.61,0:04:59.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Money
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.40,0:05:00.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:00.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.44,0:05:01.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:01.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,children
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.36,0:05:04.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是时候盛大揭幕钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.36,0:05:04.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's time for the grand unveiling of Money
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.84,0:05:06.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说  蟹堡乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.84,0:05:06.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, Krabby Land
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.53,0:05:10.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小朋友们  现在跟蟹叔叔保证
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:10.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, kids, now promise Uncle Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.81,0:05:12.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是你们玩的时候饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.81,0:05:12.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that if you get hungry while you're playing
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.75,0:05:14.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们就进蟹堡王里面买既美味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:14.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you'll come inside for some delicious
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.68,0:05:16.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又营养的蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.68,0:05:16.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,nutritious Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.71,0:05:19.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们保证
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.71,0:05:19.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We promise
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.50,0:05:23.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那好  揭幕了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:23.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, here we go
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.12,0:05:24.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为大家献上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.12,0:05:24.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I give you
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.03,0:05:26.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.03,0:05:26.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby Land
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:31.47,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(262,778)}欢乐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:33.52,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(784,572)}堡垒探险
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:35.18,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(300,872)}水管世界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.18,0:05:36.81,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1126,698)}面包机马术
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.81,0:05:39.02,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1010,908)}梦幻火箭船
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.46,0:05:44.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.46,0:05:44.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.97,0:05:47.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.97,0:05:47.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That reminds me
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.23,0:05:49.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,忘了给你们这些涂色书
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.23,0:05:49.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I forgot to give you these coloring books
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.03,0:05:50.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,兼免责条款了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.03,0:05:50.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,slash liability waivers
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.98,0:05:52.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要交回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.98,0:05:52.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone who hands theirs back
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.70,0:05:56.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就可以看到独一无二的蟹堡堡小丑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:56.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,gets to meet the one and only Krabby the Clown
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.06,0:05:58.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.06,0:05:58.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have fun
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.89,0:06:00.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也别忘了去吃超多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.89,0:06:00.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And don't forget to eat plenty
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.07,0:06:02.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,富含维生素的蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.07,0:06:02.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of vitamin-enriched Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.00,0:06:03.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡堡小丑最爱吃这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:03.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby the Clown's favorite meal
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.87,0:06:07.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要蟹堡堡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.87,0:06:07.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We want Krabby
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.61,0:06:09.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡堡在哪  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.61,0:06:09.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where is Krabby, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.50,0:06:12.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我数完他们钱了他才会来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.50,0:06:12.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He'll be here after I count their money
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.21,0:06:13.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拖住他们就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.21,0:06:13.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just stall them
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.55,0:06:14.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拖住他们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.55,0:06:14.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stall them?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.72,0:06:15.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么个拖法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.72,0:06:15.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How do I do that?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.98,0:06:18.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道  陪他们玩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.98,0:06:18.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know, be entertaining
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.00,0:06:24.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小朋友们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.00,0:06:24.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, kids
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.34,0:06:26.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不是蟹堡堡小丑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.34,0:06:26.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're not Krabby the Clown
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.27,0:06:27.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我确实不是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.27,0:06:27.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.46,0:06:28.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.46,0:06:28.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.89,0:06:32.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是蟹堡堡心爱的小跟班
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.89,0:06:32.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm Krabby's beloved sidekick
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.51,0:06:34.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.51,0:06:34.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.49,0:06:36.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大盗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:36.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Burglar
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.98,0:06:37.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.98,0:06:37.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lame
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.44,0:06:39.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡堡马上就会到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.44,0:06:39.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby will be here soon
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.85,0:06:40.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:40.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.52,0:06:41.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得搭公交来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.52,0:06:41.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,had to take the bus
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.99,0:06:45.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过这个时候呢  一起来玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.99,0:06:45.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But in the meantime, let's have some fun
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.67,0:06:47.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们喜欢泡泡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.67,0:06:47.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You kids like bubbles?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.59,0:06:48.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.59,0:06:48.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.63,0:06:51.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是因为你们没见过我吹的泡泡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.63,0:06:51.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you've never seen my bubbles
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.43,0:06:54.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.43,0:06:54.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Voila
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.47,0:06:56.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水母形状的泡泡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.47,0:06:56.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A bubble shaped like a jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.31,0:06:57.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:06:57.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about that?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.39,0:06:58.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:06:58.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Still lame
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.79,0:07:02.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.79,0:07:02.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.22,0:07:05.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好大吃一惊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.22,0:07:05.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Prepare to be blown back on your tail fins
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.23,0:07:10.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哒哒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.23,0:07:10.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ta-dah
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.64,0:07:15.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你太垃圾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.64,0:07:15.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You stink
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.94,0:07:17.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快带小丑来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.94,0:07:17.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bring on the clown
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.54,0:07:18.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:18.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.22,0:07:20.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在是压轴好戏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.22,0:07:20.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now for a finale
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.14,0:07:39.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:39.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.94,0:07:42.10,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(830,788)}末日坑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.73,0:07:42.98,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(244,948)}海草圈秋千
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.84,0:07:55.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们貌似对我痛苦有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.84,0:07:55.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They seem to respond to me being in pain
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.99,0:07:58.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们喜欢别人受苦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:58.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They enjoy other people's misery
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.11,0:07:59.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小朋友们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.11,0:07:59.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, kids
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.12,0:08:00.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:08:00.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Check this out
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.11,0:08:10.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于把他们控制住了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.11,0:08:10.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got them right where I want them
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:48.75,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(610,854)}利马豆
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.13,0:09:15.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.13,0:09:15.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.28,0:09:17.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我再也拖不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:17.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't take much more of this stalling stuff
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.91,0:09:20.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你老是就只想着你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.91,0:09:20.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Always thinking about yourself
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.79,0:09:22.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快出去拖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:22.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get out there and stall
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.60,0:09:24.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你胳膊跟腿怎么了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.60,0:09:24.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What happened to your arms and legs, boy?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.58,0:09:27.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小孩子拿它们当回旋镖来玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:27.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The kids are using them as boomerangs
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.32,0:09:31.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回旋镖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.32,0:09:31.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boomerangs?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.61,0:09:32.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.61,0:09:32.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.42,0:09:34.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我窗户会被砸坏的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.42,0:09:34.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They might break my windows
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.05,0:09:35.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:35.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are we going to do?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.38,0:09:37.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那既然小孩的钱都数完了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.38,0:09:37.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, now that all their money's counted
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.26,0:09:39.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就去说蟹堡堡到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:39.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,tell them Krabby has just arrived
Dialogue: 1,0:09:39.99,0:09:40.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.99,0:09:40.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.91,0:09:41.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.91,0:09:41.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's here?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.96,0:09:44.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.96,0:09:44.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy, oh, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.62,0:09:46.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快出去跟他们讲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.62,0:09:46.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get out there and tell them
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.33,0:09:49.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家听一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.33,0:09:49.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen, everybody
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.61,0:09:52.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡堡小丑已经来店里了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.61,0:09:52.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby the Clown is in the building
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.84,0:09:57.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们想要谁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.84,0:09:57.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who do you want?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.43,0:09:58.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡堡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.43,0:09:58.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.91,0:10:00.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们要他什么时候来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.91,0:10:00.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When do you want him?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.90,0:10:02.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.90,0:10:02.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.34,0:10:06.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡堡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.34,0:10:06.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.06,0:10:06.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.06,0:10:06.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.75,0:10:08.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小朋友们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:08.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, kids
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.27,0:10:10.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好见蟹堡堡小丑了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.27,0:10:10.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready to meet Krabby the Clown?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.17,0:10:13.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:13.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.34,0:10:14.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.34,0:10:14.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.94,0:10:16.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小朋友们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.94,0:10:16.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, kids
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.86,0:10:19.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢大家来捧场
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.86,0:10:19.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you all for coming
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.03,0:10:21.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.03,0:10:21.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.09,0:10:23.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要吃超多的蟹黄堡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.09,0:10:23.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eat plenty of Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.96,0:10:33.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老螃蟹  你又得手了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.96,0:10:33.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabs, you'd done it again
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.68,0:10:34.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你确实得手了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.68,0:10:34.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll say you have
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.85,0:10:35.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.85,0:10:35.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.98,0:10:37.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么能这样  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.98,0:10:37.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How could you, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.10,0:10:41.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你跟小朋友保证会有蟹堡堡小丑的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.10,0:10:41.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You promised these children Krabby the Clown
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.24,0:10:42.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我看到的却只有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:42.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But all I saw up there was
Dialogue: 1,0:10:43.97,0:10:45.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吝啬小气鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.97,0:10:45.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cheapy the Cheapskate
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.43,0:10:47.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才不吝啬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.43,0:10:47.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I ain't cheap
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.02,0:10:53.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,趁番茄还没坏赶紧拿回厨房去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.02,0:10:51.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now take this tomato
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.75,0:10:53.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,back to the kitchen before it spoils
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.58,0:10:56.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是夏天的真谛怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.58,0:10:56.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But what about the true meaning of summer?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.48,0:10:58.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小朋友怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.48,0:10:58.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What about the children?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.22,0:10:59.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.22,0:10:59.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The children?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.70,0:11:01.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才不稀罕什么小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.70,0:11:01.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't care about the children
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.57,0:11:03.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只稀罕他们家长的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.57,0:11:03.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just care about their parents' money
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.03,0:11:06.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正他们头脑简单  非常好骗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.03,0:11:05.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The fact that their feeble minds
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.68,0:11:06.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are easily manipulated
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.99,0:11:09.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿便宜游乐场跟无能小丑都唬得住
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.99,0:11:09.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,by cheap playgrounds and talentless clowns
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.79,0:11:11.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可一点也不心疼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:11.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is no skin off my nose
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.77,0:11:14.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,适者生存  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.77,0:11:14.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Survival of the fittest, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.27,0:11:16.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,适者生存
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:16.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Survival of the fittest
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.63,0:11:21.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小朋友们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.63,0:11:21.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, kids
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.01,0:11:26.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹叔叔现在得去银行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.01,0:11:26.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Uncle Krabs has to go to the bank now
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.68,0:11:27.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.68,0:11:27.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get him
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.10,0:11:34.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我估计没办法知道夏天的真谛了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.10,0:11:34.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I suppose I'll never know the true meaning of summer
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.33,0:11:35.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原本可能知道过一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.33,0:11:35.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought I knew it once
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.59,0:11:38.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,却已经很久远了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:38.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but that was a long, long time ago
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.59,0:11:39.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说的是今天早上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:39.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean this morning?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.88,0:11:40.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.88,0:11:40.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:11:42.64,0:11:45.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快出来一下  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.64,0:11:45.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come outside, Mr. Squarepants
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.25,0:11:47.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是夏天的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.25,0:11:47.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a summer miracle
Dialogue: 1,0:11:47.73,0:11:49.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.73,0:11:49.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hoorah
Dialogue: 1,0:11:49.83,0:11:52.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好几千块的钱在随风飘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.83,0:11:52.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thousands of dollars fluttering in the breeze
Dialogue: 1,0:11:52.57,0:11:56.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这应该就是夏天的真谛了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.57,0:11:56.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess that's the true meaning of summer
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.67,0:12:02.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.67,0:12:02.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.17,0:12:04.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他要错过夏天的乐趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.17,0:12:04.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's missing out on all the summer fun
Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.09,0:12:06.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放我走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.09,0:12:06.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me go
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.17,0:12:08.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得拿走那些绿绿的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.17,0:12:08.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got to get some of that green stuff
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.68,0:12:09.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.68,0:12:09.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.61,0:12:11.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是那个绿绿的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.61,0:12:11.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not that green stuff
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.89,0:12:15.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.89,0:12:15.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.62,0:12:16.00,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1040,742)}利马豆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:19.46,起司 特殊标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(363,347)}露营
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:21.30,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz27.85\pos(338,514)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:25.05,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.59,0:12:23.13,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz27.85\pos(422,546)}分镜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:25.05,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz27.85\pos(392,292)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.43,0:12:27.01,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz27.85\pos(308,398)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.43,0:12:27.01,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz27.85\pos(480,714)}创意总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.43,0:12:27.01,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.45,0:12:31.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,周末可终于到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.45,0:12:31.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Finally, the weekend is here
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.21,0:12:34.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可不是以前的那种周末
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.21,0:12:34.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and this isn't just any old weekend
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:38.94,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(696,184)}海绵宝宝去露营
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.76,0:12:38.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是海绵宝宝和派大星去露营的周末
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.76,0:12:38.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the weekend SpongeBob and Patrick go camping
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.94,0:12:42.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们在树林迷路回不来  那有多好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.94,0:12:41.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be great if they got lost in the woods
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.05,0:12:42.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and never came back?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.85,0:12:44.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  我好怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.85,0:12:44.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, I'm scared
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.97,0:12:48.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那可太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.97,0:12:48.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That would be great
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.55,0:12:50.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等了好久就为了这一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.55,0:12:50.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've waited a long time for this
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.63,0:12:51.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,软床
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.63,0:12:51.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A soft bed
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.78,0:12:52.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,热茶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.78,0:12:52.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Warm tea
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.92,0:12:54.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好书
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.92,0:12:54.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A good book
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.32,0:12:56.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有整整两天没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.32,0:12:56.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And two whole days with no
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.86,0:13:02.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:02.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.15,0:13:05.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:05.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.21,0:13:07.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个不是应该在露营吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.21,0:13:07.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,aren't you two supposed to be camping?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.29,0:13:08.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们本来就露营啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.29,0:13:08.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We are camping
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.44,0:13:12.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  营地离家十尺远不算露营
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.44,0:13:10.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, it's not camping
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:12.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if you're ten feet from your house
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.04,0:13:16.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,地点不重要  户外就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.04,0:13:14.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter where you are
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.56,0:13:16.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,as long as you're outdoors
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.15,0:13:18.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那些安逸的城里人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.15,0:13:18.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,While all those soft city folk
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.08,0:13:20.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还在安稳躺床上看书的时候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.08,0:13:20.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are safe in their beds reading books
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.19,0:13:21.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们置身此地  挑战自我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.19,0:13:21.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we're out here pitting ourselves
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.94,0:13:24.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对抗着大自然那强大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.94,0:13:24.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,against the formidable forces of nature
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.23,0:13:25.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要一起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.23,0:13:25.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You want to join us?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.35,0:13:26.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.35,0:13:26.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.07,0:13:26.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.07,0:13:26.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.74,0:13:27.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,家里面要开心点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.74,0:13:27.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have fun inside
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.72,0:13:32.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,家里面要开心点是几个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.72,0:13:32.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, have fun inside?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.57,0:13:33.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就只是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.57,0:13:33.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.31,0:13:34.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,家里面开心点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.31,0:13:34.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,have fun inside
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.22,0:13:35.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明天见了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.22,0:13:35.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.31,0:13:36.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.31,0:13:36.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bye
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.10,0:13:39.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们这些小混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.10,0:13:39.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You little sneak
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.64,0:13:41.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看出来你们居心何在了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.64,0:13:41.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I see what you're doing
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.83,0:13:42.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.83,0:13:42.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.27,0:13:44.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别以为我看不出来你们想干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.27,0:13:44.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't think I can't see what you're doing
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.00,0:13:45.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.00,0:13:45.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.76,0:13:48.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们暗示我受不住这苦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.76,0:13:48.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're saying I can't take it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.02,0:13:48.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.02,0:13:48.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But all I
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.49,0:13:51.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们说我娇生惯养
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.49,0:13:51.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're saying I'm soft
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.67,0:13:55.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以为用家里面开心点这句话来唬我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.67,0:13:55.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You think your little "have fun inside" challenge
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.08,0:13:57.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就能激我跟你们一起来露营
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.08,0:13:57.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is going to make me come camping with you
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.31,0:13:59.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本就是不可能的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.31,0:13:59.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but that is never going to happen
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.80,0:14:02.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我决不可能整晚都坐这外面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.80,0:14:02.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's no way I'm going to sit out here all night
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.44,0:14:03.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,陪着你们两个废物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.44,0:14:03.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with you two losers
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.78,0:14:05.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.78,0:14:05.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So get used to it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.51,0:14:07.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.51,0:14:07.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.84,0:14:09.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,家里面要开心点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.84,0:14:09.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have fun inside
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.20,0:14:09.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:09.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.76,0:14:10.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我加进去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.76,0:14:10.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm in
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.66,0:14:12.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,倒要给你们看看什么叫露营
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.66,0:14:12.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll show you camping
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.90,0:14:15.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥要跟我们一起来露营了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.90,0:14:15.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward's going to come camping with us
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.35,0:14:20.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在你们就要看到真正的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.35,0:14:20.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now you'll see how a real
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.98,0:14:23.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,露营家是怎么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.98,0:14:23.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,outdoorsman does it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.40,0:14:25.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.40,0:14:25.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here we are
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.62,0:14:29.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的遥控自动组装帐篷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.62,0:14:29.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My remote-controlled self-assembling tent
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.61,0:14:31.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好看好好学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.61,0:14:31.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Watch and learn
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.41,0:14:39.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好棒啊  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.41,0:14:39.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was great, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.28,0:14:40.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是你要怎么进去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.28,0:14:40.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but how do you get inside?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.97,0:14:42.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  看起来破破烂烂的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.97,0:14:42.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's all crushy-looking
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.06,0:14:44.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都还没搭起来  你们这些白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.06,0:14:44.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It isn't put up yet, you idiots
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.82,0:14:50.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,个性化设计
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.82,0:14:50.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Customization
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.16,0:14:50.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天才
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.16,0:14:50.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Genius
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.01,0:14:54.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他在弄松地板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.01,0:14:54.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's tenderizing the ground
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.89,0:14:55.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.89,0:14:55.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.08,0:15:00.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,记下来  记下来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.08,0:15:00.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Write that down, write that down
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.82,0:15:06.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.82,0:15:06.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Voila
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.16,0:15:15.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过又有什么能比得过躺在星空下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.16,0:15:13.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But what could compare to just
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:15.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,lying out under the stars?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.91,0:15:21.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干活干得我都饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.91,0:15:21.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I worked up an appetite
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.19,0:15:23.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胃口都跟户外一样广大了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.19,0:15:23.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,as big as all outdoors
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.16,0:15:24.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该吃点东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.16,0:15:24.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time for a little grub
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.98,0:15:26.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看你们两个怕是要去煮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.98,0:15:26.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I suppose you two are going to stew up
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.88,0:15:28.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,树枝跟石头了  是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.88,0:15:28.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,some twigs and rocks, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.34,0:15:31.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才不是  有更好的东西吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.34,0:15:31.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, we got something even better
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.01,0:15:33.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,棉花糖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.01,0:15:33.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Marshmallows
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.24,0:15:33.66,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(314,766)}棉花王
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.89,0:15:39.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就跟宇航员吃东西一个样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.89,0:15:39.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just like the astronauts eat
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.58,0:15:43.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星呼叫海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:43.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick to SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.26,0:15:44.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能收到我信号吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.26,0:15:44.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you read me?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.35,0:15:45.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.35,0:15:45.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Over
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.86,0:15:47.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝呼叫派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.86,0:15:47.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob to Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.02,0:15:47.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已收到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.02,0:15:47.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I read you
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.69,0:15:48.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.69,0:15:48.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Over
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.15,0:15:50.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星呼叫海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.15,0:15:50.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick to SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.59,0:15:51.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我喜欢传话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.59,0:15:51.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I like going
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.16,0:15:52.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.16,0:15:52.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Over
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.61,0:15:54.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝呼叫派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.61,0:15:54.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob to Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.49,0:15:56.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.49,0:15:56.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me, too
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.25,0:16:04.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝呼叫派大星  随便吃点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.25,0:16:04.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob to Patrick, help yourself
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.54,0:16:05.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.54,0:16:05.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Over
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.13,0:16:07.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.13,0:16:07.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yummy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.63,0:16:10.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星呼叫海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.63,0:16:10.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick to SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.15,0:16:13.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美味已着陆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.15,0:16:13.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The deliciousness has landed
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.26,0:16:16.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个宇航员吃棉花糖去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.26,0:16:16.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you two astronauts can eat marshmallows
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.50,0:16:20.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可要吃一罐瑞典藤壶肉丸了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.50,0:16:20.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to have a can of Swedish barnacle balls
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.74,0:16:20.20,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(700,216)}瑞典藤壶肉丸
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.20,0:16:22.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去拿开罐器再来吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.20,0:16:22.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just as soon as I can get my can opener
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.04,0:16:22.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.04,0:16:22.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.92,0:16:25.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你走都走到这来了  还没带开罐器吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.92,0:16:25.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,didn't you take a can opener when you hiked out here?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.70,0:16:26.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凭什么这么麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.70,0:16:26.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why would I bother?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.77,0:16:28.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里才离我家十尺远
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.77,0:16:28.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're ten feet from my house
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.55,0:16:30.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可这里是荒野
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:30.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But this is the wilderness
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.53,0:16:33.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都不符合露营的精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.53,0:16:33.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It just doesn't seem to fit the camping spirit
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.45,0:16:35.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太废了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.45,0:16:35.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pretty weenie
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.48,0:16:36.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.48,0:16:36.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, all right
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.88,0:16:37.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我棉花糖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.88,0:16:37.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me a marshmallow
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.85,0:17:08.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,除了把融化的食物朝我吐之外
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:08.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, besides spitting molten foodstuffs at me
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.13,0:17:09.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们还做什么消遣的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.13,0:17:09.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what else do you do for fun?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.75,0:17:11.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:11.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.20,0:17:13.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,露营了长长一天之后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.20,0:17:13.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,after a long day of camping
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.27,0:17:17.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,唱首轻松的篝火歌放松放松还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.27,0:17:17.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's nice to unwind with a nice, relaxing campfire song
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.37,0:17:21.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我管这首叫篝火歌之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.37,0:17:21.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I call this one "The Campfire Song Song"
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.13,0:17:23.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我们围在篝火周围
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.13,0:17:23.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's gather round the campfire
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.75,0:17:25.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,唱我们的篝火歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.75,0:17:25.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And sing our campfire song
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.94,0:17:29.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是篝火的篝  篝火的火
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.94,0:17:29.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our C-A-M-P-F-I-R-E
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.02,0:17:30.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,唱歌的歌  之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.02,0:17:30.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,S-O-N-G song
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.78,0:17:33.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是以为我们唱歌速度
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.78,0:17:33.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And if you don't think that we can sing it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.69,0:17:35.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快不起来  那就错了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:35.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Faster, then you're wrong
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.55,0:17:40.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过真想唱得快  可以跟着一起唱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.55,0:17:40.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But it'll help if you just sing along
Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.97,0:17:44.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,篝火的篝  篝火的火
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.97,0:17:44.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,C-A-M-P-F-I-R-E
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.41,0:17:45.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,唱歌的歌  之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.41,0:17:45.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,S-O-N-G song
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.58,0:17:47.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,篝火的篝  篝火的火
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.58,0:17:47.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,C-A-M-P-F-I-R-E
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.12,0:17:48.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,唱歌的歌  之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.12,0:17:48.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,S-O-N-G song
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.06,0:17:49.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是以为我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.06,0:17:49.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And if you don't think that we
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.00,0:17:50.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,唱歌速度快不起来  那就错了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:50.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can sing it faster, then you are wrong
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.65,0:17:53.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过真想唱得快  可以跟着一起唱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.65,0:17:53.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But it'll help if you just sing along
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.13,0:17:56.43,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(702,244)}篝火歌之歌
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.41,0:17:54.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,篝火的篝  篝火的火
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.41,0:17:54.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,C-A-M-P-F-I-R-E
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.72,0:17:55.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,唱歌的歌  之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:17:55.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,S-O-N-G song
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.65,0:17:56.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.65,0:17:56.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.43,0:17:56.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.43,0:17:56.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Song
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.82,0:17:57.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,篝火的篝  篝火的火
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.82,0:17:57.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,C-A-M-P-F-I-R-E
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.11,0:17:58.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.11,0:17:58.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.74,0:18:00.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.74,0:18:00.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.55,0:18:05.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真想唱得快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.55,0:18:05.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It'll help
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.18,0:18:08.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以跟着一起唱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:08.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you just sing along
Dialogue: 1,0:18:12.00,0:18:13.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.00,0:18:13.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.09,0:18:16.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚刚是不是很放松啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.09,0:18:16.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, wasn't that relaxing?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.30,0:18:17.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,松个头
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.30,0:18:17.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.43,0:18:20.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这才叫放松
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.43,0:18:20.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thisis relaxing
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.08,0:18:25.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.08,0:18:25.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.39,0:18:27.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来救你  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.39,0:18:27.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll save you, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.15,0:18:33.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.15,0:18:33.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, are you all right?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.71,0:18:34.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.71,0:18:34.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.32,0:18:35.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嚼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.32,0:18:35.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Chew
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.98,0:18:37.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吞掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.98,0:18:37.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and swallow
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.16,0:18:39.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.16,0:18:39.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.68,0:18:40.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,舒服了没
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.68,0:18:40.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Better?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.55,0:18:41.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这哪舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.55,0:18:41.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Better?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.11,0:18:42.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我本来还好好的  结果你射过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.11,0:18:42.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was just fine until you launched
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.91,0:18:45.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那么个垃圾食物子弹  卡到我气管里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.91,0:18:45.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that ballistic junk food into my windpipe
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.54,0:18:46.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我必须得那样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.54,0:18:46.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I had to
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.92,0:18:50.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在这野外  竖笛吹得烂会很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.92,0:18:49.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's too dangerous to play the clarinet badly
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.39,0:18:50.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,out here in the wilderness
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.81,0:18:51.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能会招来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.81,0:18:51.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It might attract
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.02,0:18:54.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海熊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:54.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a sea bear
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.94,0:18:56.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海熊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.94,0:18:56.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A sea bear?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.93,0:18:59.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说的是不是那种
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.93,0:18:59.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean like the ones that
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.01,0:19:00.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不存在的玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.01,0:19:00.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,don't exist?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.24,0:19:01.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在讲什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.24,0:19:01.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.37,0:19:02.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本就没那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.37,0:19:02.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's no such thing
Dialogue: 1,0:19:02.92,0:19:04.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就只是虚构的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.92,0:19:04.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're just a myth
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.69,0:19:05.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.69,0:19:05.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.81,0:19:07.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海熊都很真实的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.81,0:19:07.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sea bears are all too real
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.46,0:19:09.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村调查者就这么写的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.46,0:19:09.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It says so in the Bikini Bottom Inquirer
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.79,0:19:12.17,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(648,152)}裤头村调查者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.79,0:19:12.17,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(464,668)}我跟海熊结婚了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.72,0:19:11.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟海熊结婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.72,0:19:11.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"I married a Sea Bear"?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.83,0:19:14.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  还有伪科学月刊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.83,0:19:14.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and Fake Science Monthly
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:17.30,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1146,250)}伪科学月刊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:17.30,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\a3\pos(402,448)}海熊跟童话\N是真的
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.60,0:19:17.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海熊跟童话是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.60,0:19:17.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Sea Bears and Fairytales Are Real"?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.30,0:19:20.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是我听过最傻的玩意了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.30,0:19:20.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's the stupidest thing I've ever heard
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.90,0:19:22.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能是傻没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.90,0:19:22.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe it is stupid
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.70,0:19:24.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是也还笨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.70,0:19:24.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but it's also dumb
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.71,0:19:25.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星说得对  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.71,0:19:25.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick's right, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.98,0:19:27.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海熊的事可不是闹着玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.98,0:19:27.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sea Bears are no laughing matter
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.60,0:19:29.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我从前认识了这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:29.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, once I met this guy who knew this guy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.00,0:19:40.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,认识的这个人认识的这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.00,0:19:40.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who knew this guy who knew this guy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.01,0:19:41.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,认识的这个人的表亲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.01,0:19:41.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who knew this guy's cousin
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.42,0:19:42.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.42,0:19:42.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're right
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.86,0:19:45.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我应该要更小心一点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.86,0:19:45.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I should be more careful
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.02,0:19:47.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实啊  要不你们说说看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.02,0:19:47.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In fact, why don't you tell me
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.37,0:19:49.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不应该做什么事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.37,0:19:49.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,all of the things I shouldn't do
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.10,0:19:51.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样才不会招来海熊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.10,0:19:51.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if I want to keep the sea bears away
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.50,0:19:52.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  简单
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:52.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, that's easy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.44,0:19:54.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,首先不要吹竖笛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.44,0:19:54.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,First off, don't play the clarinet
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.17,0:19:55.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.17,0:19:55.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, then what?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.29,0:19:57.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要特别快地来回晃手电筒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.29,0:19:57.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never wave your flashlight back and forth really fast
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.72,0:19:59.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,手电筒是它们的猎物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.72,0:19:59.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Flashlights are their natural prey
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.81,0:20:00.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.81,0:20:00.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're kidding
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.73,0:20:01.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要乱跺脚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.73,0:20:01.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't stomp around
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.61,0:20:02.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会被当作挑衅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.61,0:20:02.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They take that as a challenge
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.70,0:20:03.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.70,0:20:03.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.47,0:20:04.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,继续
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.47,0:20:04.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go on
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.43,0:20:05.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要吃奶酪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.43,0:20:05.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't ever eat cheese
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.72,0:20:06.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,切片的还是成块的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.72,0:20:06.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sliced or cubed?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.52,0:20:08.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成块
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.52,0:20:08.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cubed
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.89,0:20:09.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,切片的没事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.89,0:20:09.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sliced is fine
Dialogue: 1,0:20:09.83,0:20:10.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.83,0:20:10.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.52,0:20:11.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.52,0:20:11.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.02,0:20:12.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要戴宽边帽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.02,0:20:12.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never wear a sombrero
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.41,0:20:13.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,戴成傻子那样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.41,0:20:13.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in a goofy fashion
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.65,0:20:14.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要穿小丑鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.65,0:20:14.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or clown shoes
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.42,0:20:15.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要穿圈环裙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.42,0:20:15.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or a hoop skirt
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.28,0:20:16.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有千万
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.28,0:20:16.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And never
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.17,0:20:16.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.17,0:20:16.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ever
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.94,0:20:17.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:17.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ever
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.46,0:20:20.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,像黑猩猩那样尖叫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.46,0:20:20.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Screech like a chimpanzee
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.01,0:20:24.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好多东西可以引来海熊  太强了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.01,0:20:24.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's amazing how many things can set a sea bear off
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.26,0:20:27.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海熊特可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.26,0:20:27.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're horrible
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.12,0:20:27.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:27.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.82,0:20:32.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且我突然感觉我们都有危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.82,0:20:32.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and suddenly, I have the sense we're all in danger
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.48,0:20:33.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.48,0:20:33.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.86,0:20:35.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.86,0:20:35.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.23,0:20:38.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.23,0:20:38.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just a feeling
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.52,0:20:39.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.52,0:20:39.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.53,0:20:40.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.53,0:20:40.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.34,0:20:40.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:40.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.86,0:20:44.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.86,0:20:44.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, please don't
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.58,0:20:50.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.58,0:20:50.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, what are we going to do?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.45,0:20:52.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肯定会有海熊来吃我们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.45,0:20:52.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A sea bear is sure to come and eat us
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.41,0:20:53.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别担心  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.41,0:20:53.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.33,0:20:56.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来在土里画个防海熊圈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.33,0:20:56.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll draw us an anti-sea bear circle in the dirt
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.88,0:20:57.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好办法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.88,0:20:57.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good thinking
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.91,0:20:59.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所有专家都说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.91,0:20:59.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All the experts say
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.15,0:21:01.32,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1012,436)}伪科学月刊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.15,0:21:01.32,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(462,784)}如何防海熊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.15,0:21:01.32,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(356,532)}独家
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.17,0:21:01.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是防御海熊攻击的唯一办法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.17,0:21:01.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's the only defense against a sea bear attack
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.72,0:21:06.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们实在太好骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.72,0:21:06.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You guys are so gullible
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.13,0:21:06.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看见没
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.13,0:21:06.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.95,0:21:10.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能引来海熊的所有事我都做了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.95,0:21:10.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I did everything that attracts a sea bear
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.08,0:21:12.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,结果什么都没发生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.08,0:21:12.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and nothing happened
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.06,0:21:15.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是真的有海熊  怎么一只都没出现
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.06,0:21:15.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If sea bears really exist, why didn't one show up?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.42,0:21:16.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.42,0:21:16.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's because
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.48,0:21:19.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你没把宽边帽戴成傻子那样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.48,0:21:19.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you're not wearing your sombrero in a goofy fashion
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.73,0:21:20.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.73,0:21:20.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.63,0:21:22.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可真傻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.63,0:21:22.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How silly of me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.30,0:21:24.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是说要这样子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.30,0:21:24.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean like this?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.53,0:21:29.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.53,0:21:29.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.13,0:21:29.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要那样子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.13,0:21:29.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like that
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.84,0:21:45.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.84,0:21:45.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, are you okay?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.80,0:21:47.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.80,0:21:47.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.26,0:21:48.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.26,0:21:48.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quick
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.75,0:21:52.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,趁海熊没回来跳进防海熊圈里来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.75,0:21:50.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jump inside our anti-sea bear circle
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.83,0:21:52.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,before he comes back
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.44,0:21:52.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.44,0:21:52.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.93,0:21:55.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海熊的攻击经常不止一次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.93,0:21:55.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sea bears often attack more than once
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.42,0:21:56.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们疯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.42,0:21:56.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you crazy?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.88,0:21:59.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,土里画的圈才防不住那种怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.88,0:21:59.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A dirt circle won't stop that monster
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.79,0:22:01.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要逃命去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.79,0:22:01.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm running for my life
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.73,0:22:02.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.73,0:22:02.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.41,0:22:09.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要跑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.41,0:22:09.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't run
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.41,0:22:10.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海熊不喜欢那样子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.41,0:22:10.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sea bears hate that
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.95,0:22:13.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多谢提醒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.95,0:22:13.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the tip
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.91,0:22:16.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看我得瘸着走回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.91,0:22:16.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll just limp home, then
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.52,0:22:18.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.52,0:22:18.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.34,0:22:27.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海熊比起跑来更讨厌瘸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.34,0:22:27.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They hate limping more than running
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.90,0:22:30.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那好吧  我看我得
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.90,0:22:30.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I'll just have
Dialogue: 1,0:22:35.31,0:22:37.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚刚忘了警告你不能爬
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.31,0:22:37.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I should have warned you about crawling
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.65,0:22:44.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这回又干什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.65,0:22:44.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What did I do that time?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:44.84,0:22:45.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.84,0:22:45.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.61,0:22:47.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该是它不喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.61,0:22:47.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess he just doesn't like you
Dialogue: 1,0:22:47.72,0:22:49.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,假装成别的什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:49.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pretend to be somebody else
Dialogue: 1,0:22:49.97,0:22:51.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给  画个圈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.97,0:22:51.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, draw a circle
Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.63,0:22:52.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.63,0:22:52.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:22:58.83,0:23:00.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个是椭圆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.83,0:23:00.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was an oval
Dialogue: 1,0:23:00.74,0:23:03.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得是圈才行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.74,0:23:03.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It has to be a circle
Dialogue: 1,0:23:03.00,0:23:04.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让开
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.00,0:23:04.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Move over
Dialogue: 1,0:23:16.77,0:23:17.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有用
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.77,0:23:17.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It worked
Dialogue: 1,0:23:17.98,0:23:20.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们救了我的命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.98,0:23:20.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You guys saved my life
Dialogue: 1,0:23:20.42,0:23:23.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.42,0:23:23.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:23:23.34,0:23:24.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.34,0:23:24.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:23:24.17,0:23:26.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真高兴只是海熊而已
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.17,0:23:26.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm glad it was just a sea bear
Dialogue: 1,0:23:26.01,0:23:28.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个圈可挡不了海犀牛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.01,0:23:28.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This circle would never hold back a sea rhinoceros
Dialogue: 1,0:23:28.86,0:23:30.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么东西会引来海犀牛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.86,0:23:30.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What attracts them?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:30.37,0:23:32.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海熊攻击的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.37,0:23:32.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The sound of a sea bear attack
Dialogue: 1,0:23:34.07,0:23:35.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,幸好我们三个都穿着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.07,0:23:35.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good thing we're all wearing
Dialogue: 1,0:23:35.41,0:23:38.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,防海犀牛内衣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.41,0:23:38.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,our anti-sea rhinoceros undergarments
Dialogue: 1,0:23:38.13,0:23:39.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对吧  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.13,0:23:39.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right, Squidward?
